I trust you had a pleasant journey.

5
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,367
Do you have it?

6
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,889
Yes. It's over there.

7
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,081
When do we blow the stadium?

8
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:24,487
This evening at six.

9
