All arranged.

11
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,685
And then what?

12
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:40,050
Then I visit The Pale King.

13
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:43,848
A toast, my friend.

14
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,927
To Death!

15
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,406
Bottoms up.

16
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,521
Meet me in the square!

17
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:09,724
<i>I've been here before.</i>

18
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:17,203
<i>But always hit the floor.</i>

19
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:22,601
<i>I've spent a lifetime running.</i>

20
00:13:22,679 --> 00:13:26,365
<i>And I always get away.</i>

21
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:30,125
<i>But with you
I'm feeling something.</i>

22
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:33,885
<i>That makes me want to stay.</i>

23
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:40,246
<i>If I risk it all.</i>

24
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:47,561
<i>Could you break my fall?</i>

25
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:51,801
<i>How do I live? How do I breathe?</i>

26
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:55,248
<i>When you're not here
I'm suffocating.</i>

27
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:58,846
<i>I want to feel love
run through my blood.</i>

28
00:13:58,919 --> 00:14:02,765
<i>Tell me is this
where I give it all up?</i>

29
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:10,086
<i>For you I have to risk it all</i>

30
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:17,124
<i>'Cause the writing's on the wall.</i>

31
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:27,441
<i>A million shards of glass.</i>

32
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:34,726
<i>That haunt me from my past.</i>

33
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:39,726
<i>As the stars begin to gather.</i>

34
00:14:39,799 --> 00:14:43,407
<i>And the light begins to fade.</i>

35
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:47,040
<i>When all hope begins to shatter.</i>

36
